content.en:
The course will endeavor to encompass the following topics:
(i) Unconstrained Optimization;
(ii) Least Squares;
(iii) The Gradient Method;
(iv) Newton‘s Method;
(v) Convex Sets and Functions;
(vi) Convex Optimization;
(vii) Optimality Conditions for Linearly Constrained Problems.

